Critter, this is digital-looking enough that it could be a typeface, but on the other hand it seems simple enough that it is more likely hand drawn.
With almost 120 reads to your posts, I guess it's pretty obvious no-one has a clue. The chances that this is a typeface and not a custom design become pretty slim.
